Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:09.52,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.52,0:00:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the Witch Cult's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.94,0:00:13.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.56,0:00:15.34,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Is anyone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.34,0:00:17.55,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:23.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is that intense smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.29,0:00:39.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,P-Patrasche!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.40,0:00:44.35,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.96,0:00:48.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,A flower like this couldn't actually exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.84,0:00:51.61,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And Patrasche wouldn't just let me die...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.96,0:00:55.41,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Which means... This is an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.41,0:00:58.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's all make-believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.72,0:01:12.42,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,A lesser spirit? Did you come to help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.04,0:01:15.80,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.50,0:01:19.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It was you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.56,0:01:22.56,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,That spiteful tone means it's definitely you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.40,0:01:25.88,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot imagine my subconscious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.88,0:01:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,creating such a realistic imitation of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.86,0:01:33.53,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,This is a bewitching spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.84,0:01:37.86,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Only you and I have returned to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.34,0:01:39.95,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,How did you make it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:42.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I burned a flower in my illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.36,0:01:43.54,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.95,0:01:46.50,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Someone put a suggestion \Non the flower's scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.71,0:01:51.50,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:53.42,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,The glow of my little buds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:57.17,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I will teach everyone how to break \Nout of the bewitching spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:01:59.72,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,In... Nes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:11.81,Default,Mimi,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hi-ho! Hi-ho! No one's here! Where am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:13.73,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I've strayed away... No, \Nwe've been pulled apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:15.07,Default,JUlius,0000,0000,0000,,Is his affinity too great?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:15.82,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This is bad! If I don't do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:18.36,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Take a deep breath \Nand endure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:18.70,Default,Ricardo,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No, this is awful! No matter how much \Nforest I destroy, nothin' changes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:20.82,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot spare the energy to \Nfine-tune it just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:20.82,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}For this to happen at a time \Nlike this... Crusch-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:24.03,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Bringing everyone back is our priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:40.05,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,That will be quite enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:46.22,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't accept this disgrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:05:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.60,0:04:23.31,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,And? What is the meaning of all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.31,0:04:25.53,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Barusu, you'll explain it to me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.79,0:04:28.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'd like to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:31.11,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who attacked us first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.11,0:04:32.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:35.24,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't have to \Nask what I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.24,0:04:37.86,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,It's rich, coming from an ingrate like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:38.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ingrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:40.75,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,You are, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:43.80,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,After everything Roswaal-sama did for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:47.64,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Once you're done with him, you'd rush \Nto wag your tail for another master.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:50.39,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on! I think you're \Nmixing up your stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:53.68,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what it means to bite \Nthe hand that feeds you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.07,0:04:56.19,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me... The handwritten letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote you a letter about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:04:59.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it delivered to the mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:03.03,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I did get a letter from the capital,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:03.82,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:08.45,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,It was quite amusing, \Nsending me a blank letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:10.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,A blank letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:12.99,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,To send a blank letter
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.98,0:05:15.08,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,is a metaphor that means you have
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no intention of speaking to the recipient.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:20.96,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,It could easily be interpreted \Nas a declaration of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:23.34,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This is a huge misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:25.88,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Do I even look that clever to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:29.22,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what it means to bite \Nthe hand that feeds you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:30.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're still saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:32.10,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say it enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:34.56,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,But I get the gist now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:37.52,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,The blank letter was some kind of mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:39.63,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,and you are still Emilia-sama's dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:41.07,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:42.73,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Not really, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:46.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, sure. Dogs are like family, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:48.66,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine as a dog if I belong to Emilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:52.95,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Would you not say that standard is a bit low?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:55.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, these guys are reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:06:00.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,We pulled them together to \Nwipe out the Witch's Cult.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:02.17,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to start by evacuating the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:16.60,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru, they seem rather uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:18.52,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Remember to be considerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:22.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:24.11,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen you guys in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:27.65,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I know this is sudden,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I need to ask you all a favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:34.19,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It seems mabeasts are up to no \Ngood in the nearby forest again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:38.50,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So I've brought some specialists \Nto exterminate them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:40.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But while they're working,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you all to leave the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:44.67,Default,Head,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to fool us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:50.05,Default,Head,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to sound cheerful about this, \Nbut the villagers are frightened!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:53.55,Default,Head,0000,0000,0000,,All along, we've been afraid the \NWitch's Cult would try something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:55.93,Default,Ketty,0000,0000,0000,,The Witch's Cult? No one told me about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:56.87,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:57.30,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:58.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Why lie about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:07:00.31,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's trying to hide something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:04.78,Default,Head,0000,0000,0000,,You don't deny it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:06.98,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Then, it was true!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:09.49,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Why would they bother a \Nremote village like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:12.03,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Why else? Because of that half-elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:16.12,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Because this domain's lord is endorsing \Nthat half-elf for ruler!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:19.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to make it about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:21.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The half-elf thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:23.61,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Emilia has nothing to do with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:25.54,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She has everything to do with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:28.38,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,If you mess with a half-elf, \Nthe Witch's Cult shows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:31.43,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Even the village children know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:36.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You guys seriously believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:39.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That it's the fault of the half-elf \Nin the mansion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:44.48,Default - flashback,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,The village, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:48.44,Default - flashback,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,561)}But it might cause trouble for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:55.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean I'm just being selfish again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:02.71,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,"Lift your head. Don't look down."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Crusch-sama would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:06.13,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:09.55,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think what you're doing is wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:12.26,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,If not, there's no reason to look down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:15.14,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it harder to lift your head here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,than to throw a tantrum in the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:19.60,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Now, listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:25.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to that, this is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:29.86,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I understand your feelings and \Nconcerns very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:33.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell you to try to change them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:35.16,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously, you'll have your own opinions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:38.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts, but I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:42.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But for now, please accept my request.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:43.79,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Please do as I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:46.13,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Staying in the village is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:52.13,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,The words of my household's employee
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:55.22,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,are those of our master, \NRoswaal-sama, himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.09,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ram...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:58.97,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Follow his instructions immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:06.44,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me back there. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:07.60,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:08.36,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:12.86,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Having you take my side so easily \Nis kind of a new feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:14.53,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean you've acknowledged me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:17.99,Default,Petra,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:20.91,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Petra... What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:25.75,Default,Petra,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, will the lady from the \Nmansion run away with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:26.75,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:30.67,Default,Petra,0000,0000,0000,,She came to the village yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.05,Default,Petra,0000,0000,0000,,She told us
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:34.86,Default,Petra,0000,0000,0000,,we should take refuge in the mansion because
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's dangerous here, just like you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:41.64,Default,Petra,0000,0000,0000,,But no one in the village \Nwould listen to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:44.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:47.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,She wouldn't get mad or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you should hurry and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:49.90,Default,Petra,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:55.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Emilia after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:59.32,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,You should know that she isn't \Nso perceptive as to back down
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the moment someone denies her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:06.79,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But I also know she's not the kind of girl \Nwho wouldn't be hurt by mean words.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:10.42,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,She tried to convince the villagers \Nto leave, but they refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:12.67,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,But she couldn't do nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:15.34,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,so she repaired the forest barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:18.51,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,She feared there might be a mabeast attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:22.89,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,In and of itself, that's not a \Nbad decision, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:26.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Julius...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:28.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:32.40,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to explain things to Emilia \Nand the loli in the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:36.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,With you there, it'll be more convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:40.95,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Just take it as a sign of my repentance \Nfor going nuts in the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:44.18,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:47.45,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,If that will help the discussion \Nto go more smoothly,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:49.04,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,do not hesitate to use me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:51.13,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:55.50,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who put a \Nspirit on me, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:57.13,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Explain that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:11:00.47,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I get that you're a spirit arts user.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:04.26,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,More precisely, I prefer to \Nbe called a "spirit knight."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:05.93,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I do use the spirit arts, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:10.19,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,But that has not prevented me \Nfrom training with the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:14.44,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And you were the one who set \Nthe little red one on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:17.23,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,"Set it on you" is a harsh way to put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:22.24,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I was only having her, \NIa, secretly protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:25.95,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what was that thing you \Ndid when you broke the illusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:29.25,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,A high class of magic known as "Nect."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:32.42,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,It connects the gates \Nof all who are in range,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:34.13,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,so they can communicate with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:38.19,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,However, it appeared to work \Na bit too well on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:41.22,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was about to lose myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:44.14,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,For the spirits to mistake \Nthe tuning is unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:48.89,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,You may have a strong affinity \Nwith spirits, perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:55.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sadly, the only spirit I ever made \Nfriends with was a gray cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:12:00.07,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Did you patch things up with Julius?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:01.45,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Did it work out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:03.16,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking that matter back with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to mull over carefully before I \Nmake an optimistic decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:09.45,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Come to the mansion with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:12.29,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll need at least one person from \Nthe Crusch camp with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to smooth over the misunderstanding \Nwith the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:18.34,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do that after I finish my work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.80,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-{\i1}kyun{\i0}, come help us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:23.01,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous work \Ninvolving the Witch's Cult.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:26.30,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,The contract said he'd buy their \Ncargo at the asking price,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:28.85,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,so we must thoroughly inspect the goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:32.35,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But that shouldn't be our job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:33.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this more importa—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:34.73,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:39.48,Default,Ketty,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey... No lovers' quarrels \Nin my carriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:43.28,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Hee-hee! You got in trouble, Subaru-{\i1}kyun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:45.99,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Really, what a troublemaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.83,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,There. He lowered his guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:55.62,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's one of the Witch's Cult.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.62,0:12:57.88,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,I touched him earlier to confirm it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:13:00.05,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,A weird spell is implanted in him,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just like the "fingers" \Nof the Sin Archbishops.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:04.47,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,One was among the merchants?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:08.35,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I stole into his carriage, \Nto get under his guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:13.56,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Now, tell us all the details concerning \Nwhat you're plotting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:16.50,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,My hands are the gentlest in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:18.90,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,but they can do some nasty things, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:20.82,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:23.53,Default,Ketty,0000,0000,0000,,...right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:25.15,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Ia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:26.91,Default,Ketty,0000,0000,0000,,And now, it's the beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:26.49,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Protect him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:28.70,Default,Ketty,0000,0000,0000,,of the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:15:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:43.35,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness... You're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.85,0:13:46.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Why are... you dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:48.43,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,I had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't reproduce clothes with healing magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:53.94,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless, given the situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you and Felis are all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.28,0:13:58.44,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Run 'em off! Don't back down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.49,0:14:04.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,How did they get into the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:07.29,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,They stowed away in the carriages.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.29,0:14:09.20,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,There was a finger among the merchants,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we didn't take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:12.03,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:14.92,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,This is not the time for regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:18.71,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,We had Tivey and Madame Ram evacuate \Nto the mansion with the injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:21.43,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Felis, join them and heal who you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:22.43,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.22,0:14:26.89,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's crush all the \Nfingers that are left!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:36.45,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,To think, to think, to think, to think!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:38.73,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That you would resist us this much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:50.32,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Such tenacity, clinging to this \Never-increasing love...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:55.70,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,As a diligent disciple, I cannot \Nbegin to express my respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:58.68,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! My brain trembles!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:14:59.46,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,You're mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:09.56,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,In battle, if one focuses on what \Nthe unseen arm does,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:12.26,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,one will fail to see what is visible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:14.43,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That is sloth, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.65,0:15:16.47,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.78,0:15:27.12,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,He self-destructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:28.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wilhelm-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.62,0:15:33.33,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,We can't leave you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've gotta get you to Felis!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.23,0:15:36.29,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:40.96,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why? Why? Why? Why? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:44.35,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.35,0:15:48.55,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,After the attack you just endured... Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:52.76,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Why do you not bend to my diligence?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.02,0:15:54.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,At a time like this... And they keep coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:55.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.77,0:15:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what you're looking for, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.98,0:16:00.86,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's a gift from your precious witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.86,0:16:03.99,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,You thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.99,0:16:06.77,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,You really did have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:08.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Quit shouting...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.18,0:16:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep yelling at me like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:11.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,it'll make my brain tremble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:14.32,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,You must
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:15.50,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.79,0:16:19.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Julius, we'll handle things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:21.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You take care of your end!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:22.93,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And take care of Wilhelm-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:25.26,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,That is quite a vague order,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:30.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Julius...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:33.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it can wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:38.70,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait! Wait! Wait! Wait! Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, right there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:44.61,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,You cowardly, foolish, insolent, little man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.95,0:16:49.87,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where you try to run, it's futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.66,0:16:54.11,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,What do you expect to find at \Nwherever you're running to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:04.84,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,At long last, it would seem the end has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:07.25,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Do you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:09.13,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,know what this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.18,0:17:13.39,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's a magic stone for creating barriers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:16.35,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,They were stashed in trees \Nthroughout the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.35,0:17:17.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:22.39,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.24,0:17:33.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This area is a mabeast breeding ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:35.61,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,and we're a prime feast for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.37,0:17:39.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,At least, if you don't have one \Nof Emilia's barrier stones!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:48.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Only one finger left now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:50.79,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Once we get rid of that one...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.56,0:17:58.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... We have to hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.60,0:18:00.05,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:02.43,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:08.48,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! My brain trembles!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:15.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sloth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.58,0:18:18.36,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.01,0:18:32.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Emilia...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:35.18,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Stand down, villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.64,0:18:38.55,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow you to do such wicked things!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.77,0:18:43.05,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah... Ah! How grand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:46.03,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What a grand day! What a lucky day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.03,0:18:48.57,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What a grand destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.57,0:18:49.44,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Emilia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:50.06,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:52.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I... I can't wait around now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.49,0:18:54.73,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You want to make Emilia fight him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.93,0:18:55.82,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a little faith in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:19:01.46,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,The people you want to protect
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.46,0:19:03.95,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,are not just those behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:12.33,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.68,0:19:16.55,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,My witch! My love's guide!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.75,0:19:20.97,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,I don't blame you for being charmed \Nby my beloved daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:23.09,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,but I won't allow any\Nunwanted pests around her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:31.19,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Naïve!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:34.74,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Naïve! Naïve! Naïve! Naïve! \NNaïve, naïve, naïve, naïve, naïve, naïve!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.62,0:19:41.93,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is love's true ending...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:43.69,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The fruit of my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.69,0:19:47.20,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Proof that the witch has returned my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:49.42,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,That proof doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.42,0:19:52.09,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Your crush is purely one-sided.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.01,0:19:55.63,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.68,0:20:06.15,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this is true... true diligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.15,0:20:10.64,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for being defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:31.92,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,See? Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:36.26,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,We've now eliminated all the fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:38.47,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Victory is ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.39,0:20:43.60,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally over...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.69,0:20:52.27,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Go see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:54.11,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.45,0:21:06.79,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-{\i1}kyun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:14.71,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.30,0:21:17.88,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,From Emilia... From everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.14,0:21:21.88,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-{\i1}kyun{\i0}, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.88,0:21:23.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.18,0:21:24.22,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:25.18,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.02,0:21:28.89,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Julius, stay away from—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.73,0:21:32.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.11,0:21:38.65,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,The moment Ia was flung from his \Nbody, I had a bad feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:39.86,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:40.48,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,That
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.37,0:21:42.87,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,isn't Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.91,0:21:44.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.87,0:21:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a Sin Archbishop of the Witch's \NCult, representing Sloth...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.04,0:21:52.66,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Betelgeuse Romanée-Conti!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:58.17,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.17,0:22:00.95,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What a fantastic body this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.95,0:22:04.16,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's been decades since I had \Na body that fit me so well!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.16,0:22:05.09,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,You madman!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.20,0:22:07.50,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of that body right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.93,0:22:09.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Madman?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.18,0:22:13.04,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I am driven mad with love.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.02,0:22:16.34,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Generous love, respectful love, pure love,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.34,0:22:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,tender love, familial love, \Nerotic love, friendly love!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.04,0:22:22.66,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Love, love, love... Love! Love! Love! Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.66,0:22:25.86,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.75,0:22:29.96,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.96,0:22:31.33,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.58,0:22:36.16,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This body is already under \Nmy subconscious control.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.16,0:22:39.88,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Realize what you're about to do, Subaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.88,0:22:42.34,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what you returned here to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.01,0:22:44.51,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.51,0:22:49.34,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "what" me... You moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.81,0:22:54.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I am Betelgeuse Romanée-Conti...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.05,0:22:56.52,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This body has already become my finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:23:00.89,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I'm Natsuki Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.33,0:23:03.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me, Julius.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.14,0:23:04.97,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Use your sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.97,0:23:06.58,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.58,0:23:10.91,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't stop me now, we can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.35,0:23:13.09,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Before that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.09,0:23:15.64,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,No, Subaru! I cannot do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.64,0:23:17.44,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,You told me, "It can wait."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.94,0:23:20.25,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't there something\Nyou meant to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:24.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... It looks like \NI won't get the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.68,0:23:26.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Felis!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.49,0:23:29.34,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.83,0:23:37.77,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,You can resent me for this, Subaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.44,0:23:39.94,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,I will, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.25,0:23:48.99,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Felis!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.99,0:23:51.07,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,No one else can do it, can they?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.46,0:23:54.27,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,This is what Subaru-{\i1}kyun{\i0} wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.15,0:23:56.11,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.11,0:23:58.58,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,You think I did that\Nbecause I wanted to?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.58,0:24:00.48,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,To use my power for Crusch-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.48,0:24:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the power I swore to our leader, for this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.94,0:24:06.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it can't be, it can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.78,0:24:11.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Just when I'd found such a perfect vessel...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.99,0:24:14.80,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,My lack of virtue was what forced this \Nundesirable decision on you and Felis.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.12,0:24:14.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Just when the Ordeal's completion \Nwas at hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.53,0:24:17.72,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,One day, I'm sure I will be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.18,0:24:21.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I will never die...
